### Who am I (sanity)
GET {{HOST}}/api/v1/auth/whoami
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Accept: application/json

### Plaid ping
GET {{HOST}}/api/v1/plaid/ping
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Accept: application/json

### Create Plaid link_token (frontend will use this)
POST {{HOST}}/api/v1/plaid/link/token/create
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{}

### Exchange public_token (paste the value you get from Plaid Link)
POST {{HOST}}/api/v1/plaid/public-token/exchange
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "publicToken": "{{PUBLIC_TOKEN}}"
}

### List your Plaid items (useful to grab the UUID for sync)
GET {{HOST}}/api/v1/plaid/items
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Accept: application/json

### Accounts for one item (set @ITEM_ID at top)
GET {{HOST}}/api/v1/plaid/items/{{ITEM_ID}}/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Accept: application/json

### Run transactions sync for one item (cursor-based)
POST {{HOST}}/api/v1/plaid/items/{{ITEM_ID}}/sync
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Accept: application/json

### Verify transactions persisted (first page)
GET {{HOST}}/api/v1/transactions?page=0&size=20&sort=date,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Accept: application/json